law.history: Repealed 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 371, sec. 64, effective July 15, 1996; amended 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 371, sec. 23. -- Created 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 512, Pt. 1, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1996.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/96). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 371, sec. 64, prevails over its amendment in 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 371, sec. 23.
